long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Play the classic Snake game in your browser!

A simple snake game for when you're bored.
Choose your color and start the game.
Use the arrow keys to move.
Eat the food to grow bigger and avoid hitting the wall or yourself.
Set the greatest highscore and compete with your friends.
Turn the sound off with mute icon.
